🎙️ Speech Emotion Recognition using Deep Learning
Built a deep learning-based system to classify 8 emotional states from Hindi speech using the IITKGP-SEHSC dataset.

🔍 Features extracted: MFCC, Chroma, Mel Spectrogram, ZCR

🧠 Models used: CNN, LSTM, CNN-LSTM Hybrid

📊 Achieved 78.17% accuracy in emotion classification

💡 Applications: Virtual assistants, mental health monitoring, emotion-aware AI

Tech Stack: Python, Librosa, TensorFlow/Keras, NumPy, Matplotlib
